  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct used in posterior thoracolumbar spinal fixation. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below required level due to a single test condition being evaluated. Intended use is limited to static, non-cannulated constructs under compression-bending loading in the context of regulatory submission supporting a 510(k) predicate comparison.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-f1717-noncannulated-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-fea-pedicle-screw-ensemble-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-lab1-experimental-n11",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-lab2-experimental-n11"
  ],
